{"type": "article", "id": 17433, "title": "带锂电池的钱包", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-12T06:43:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607183501Fhnz57eBSCa0oZkT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t临时出门往往没有充够手机，多带一个移动电源又嫌太麻烦，这个自带电池的钱包专门解决临时充电的问题。它在钱包的折叠处隐藏了非常小的锂电池，上面有微型的USB接口，可以连接上 iPhone 手机。电池里有 2400mAh 的容量，足够 iPhone6s 充满一次电。所以只需拿着手机和钱包就可以上路了。售价 80 美元，<a href=\"http://www.hellonomad.com/products/wallet\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144549pEO6RaLSV7xKouF1.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1142\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.05740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144549oSYMXdrkvZBpxiNL.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1754\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144550PpEykxM7BChDqONb.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"251\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.41833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144550qZQEPgIxUjhmd0cC.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"398\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}